fm: int integerBreak(int n)      {         if (n==2) return 1;         if (n==3) return 2;         vector<int>dp(n+1,0);         dp[2] = 2;         dp[3] = 3;         for (int i=4; i<=n; i++)         {             int temp = 0;             for (int j=2; j<=i/2; j++)             {                 if (dp[j]*dp[i-j]>temp)                     temp = dp[j]*dp[i-j];             }             dp[i] = temp;         }         return dp[n];     }

fm: int findNthDigit(int N)      {         int k = 0;         long n = N;         long nums = 0;         while (n > 0)         {                     k++;                 nums = kDigitNums(k);             n -= nums;         }          if (n==0) return 9;          n += nums;         int m = n/k;         if (n%k==0) m--;         int r = n%k;         if (r==0) r=k;          int ret = pow(10,k-1) + m;         return to_string(ret)[r-1] - '0';     }
